Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要左右盖亚的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全凭你们的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石发光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在干嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人…梵大人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的引力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源点能源流入72
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果律检验装置灵敏度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力稳定,所有机能正常运作中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运震动器抵达临界点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源点能源填充100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆动律于0.3许可范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一刻终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我长久以来梦想的这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让我瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想,我的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不动了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连…梵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也一起被传送过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像是在一栋,很大的建筑物当中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建筑物?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板在动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龙的命运联系在一起的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人?在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你找我们来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是命运的邀约
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将引导盖亚走向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈帝国的指导者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫多伦卡喀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到寨巴哈的中枢来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙就是寨巴哈的指导者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄就是跟着这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要杀了你就能结束盖亚的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪个时代哪个地点纷争就是会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争才是人们所拥有且无法抗拒的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人的命运你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看穿命运的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如过去的亚特兰提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会就是艾萨克?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种叫法真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克是我在地球上的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈王竟然是幻之月人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我父亲见过的那个艾萨克?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是雷恩的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是命运的引导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个可悲的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯之谜一旦揭开他就再无用处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经解开亚特兰提斯之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完成亚特兰提斯的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要到盖亚来?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没来的话大家明明都还能过着幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了,小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚也同样鲜血淋漓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染满了因争斗而流的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我来之前就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟地球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,当我还在地球的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天,我为了一个疑问而深深感到困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有物体皆存在着共通的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个物体都会产生与其质量相同的互相吸引之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是引力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股无形的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟为什么会存在于这个世间呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人与人相互吸引与相互砍杀都是世上的定数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于不停地重复死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上的一切秩序才得以维护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秩序的源头又是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规范宇宙的根源力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的命运,其定义究竟为何?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在着法则吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了解开那个谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将一切都奉献给研究与实验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究还是无法得到结论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使命在垂危我的求知欲不但没有衰退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而还变得更为强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道命运的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我回过神来,自己已来到一个陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空高挂着月亮与蓝色月亮,荒凉无尽的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里正是盖亚的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫瘠的土壤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严苛的气候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民只能采集少许的植物维生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为着重复不断的侵略而苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么残酷的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我领悟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了拯救这些人们而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将自己的一切知识,教给了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为"科学"的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战胜自然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知的科学全是为了人们而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该臣服于命运而是要亲手开创命运才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们遵从我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完成绝无仅有的理想国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我得知和创造出盖亚有关的亚特兰提斯传说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯那里有能够创造命运的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后,我将自己的全部知识投注其中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断探究其原理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后终于让我创造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够产生命运的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中亚特兰提斯之民能将人的意念转换为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而得以决定命运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,这个盖亚也是亚特兰提斯创造的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚是亚特兰提斯创造的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要敔动这具能够产生如此美好力量的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要亚特兰提斯之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须要将\N留在盖亚的能源点找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也在进攻弗雷特后已获实现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是最后的关键,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼受到命运牵引也来到了我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我长久以来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的亚特兰提斯机械
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变装置终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变装置?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么要用机械来改变命运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此让那么多人遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是为了崭新的命运而注定要牺牲的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渺小的不幸乃为广大幸福的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦完全的命运诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就能得到完全的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…根本就是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要藉由机械控制的命运得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就乖乖与我一同迎接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接人们崭新的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎么看也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回阿斯多利亚去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯也同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要扔下亚连他们不顾吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又没办法知道,他们究竟被转移到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且开着这种船到处乱晃也只是浪费时间罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,我是商人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈那群人是真的打算要毁灭盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我自己的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的思念会在某处相连在一起,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信我的思念会有实现的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变装置最后的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农制的人型装甲\N竟然拥有那样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要亲自解开这个谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能再让弗肯抢在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们并不是要杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又看到预见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地陷落,整个世界被炸开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚特兰提斯灭亡时的情景吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但规模要大得多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了盖亚的未来?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前还不能让亚特兰提斯之力重现世间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后是那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变装置一旦敔动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚很可能会步上亚特兰提斯的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了?梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们开始拆解艾斯嘉科尼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,既然你能感受到艾斯嘉科尼的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该也可以逆向操作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能将意念传达过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们没在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该还是能够操纵艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们合力一定能够办到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你也被卷入感应之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要也受这种苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去,你可能会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,在内心想着艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心地想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达过去,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?它为什么会动?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么看不到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那名少女的力量吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,我们得先离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:17:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,保护小瞳\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳就拜托你了,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从屋顶离开,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,我们上屋顶去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又看得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我们走\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很相信他是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这城市感觉好冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的人们真的过得幸福吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追来了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要我牺牲生命,我也不会把你交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,小瞳,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,可别被甩下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼,再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当龙与少女接近时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的蓝图便会产生动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球少女是说明这一切的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须拆散那两人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某物体正从首都方向接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异常迅速,进行戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈皇帝多伦卡喀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们命运的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能帮我占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有学长的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.63,0:23:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情的黄金律作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:57.21,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:05.66,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:13.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:19.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:21.80,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:26.81,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:30.65,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:34.45,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
